    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/c7f975018ff5610012cbf40d853b0d77.poster.avif?t=1761336475\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/c7f975018ff5610012cbf40d853b0d77.webm?t=1761336475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/c7f975018ff5610012cbf40d853b0d77.mp4?t=1761336475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>背景故事</strong></h2>流亡生活一片空虚，直到&quot;备用利爪&quot;成立。如今每天都有任务在等着。加入队长的复仇之旅，招募你的船员，装备你的战舰，在赚取报酬的同时推翻腐败的政权。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2>在《Kamikaze Tactics》中，你将：<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/97265fb64fc13999f81855bd20c3182f.poster.avif?t=1761336475\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/97265fb64fc13999f81855bd20c3182f.webm?t=1761336475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/97265fb64fc13999f81855bd20c3182f.mp4?t=1761336475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制定独特的策略以智胜对手。</h2>从各种具有独特能力、优势和弱点的飞行员和单位中组建你的战斗中队。<br>在战斗中，提前规划你的行动，保持位置优势并包抄敌人。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/059390250b7f804f447f1e9d89ac2e5b.poster.avif?t=1761336475\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/059390250b7f804f447f1e9d89ac2e5b.webm?t=1761336475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/059390250b7f804f447f1e9d89ac2e5b.mp4?t=1761336475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >护盾克制导弹。装甲克制动能武器。能量武器则是两者之间的平衡。</h2>战斗不仅仅在于良好的位置。你的武器装备同样重要。<br>利用各种武器系统，你需要做出决策，为每项任务选择最合适的工具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/4d6986552ab821a19db13a42295ceebc.poster.avif?t=1761336475\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/4d6986552ab821a19db13a42295ceebc.webm?t=1761336475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/4d6986552ab821a19db13a42295ceebc.mp4?t=1761336475\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >世界会反击。</h2>竞技场带有从炮火到信号干扰等各种修正因素，这些都会迫使你改变战术并考验你的掌控能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/69a22ccc5887a4977b3660b4296bf542.poster.avif?t=1761336475\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3045260/extras/69a22ccc5887a4977b3660b4296bf542.webm?t=1761336475\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >每次游戏都独一无二。</h2>每次游戏过程中，你都会遇到不同的船员，与不同的首领作战，发现更多的角色互动。",
